title: Luis Rubiales says he will resign as Spanish soccer federation president over unwanted World Cup kiss
description: Luis Rubiales says he intends to resign as president of Spain's soccer federation after Women's World Cup champion Jenni Hermoso accused him of sexual assault following the country's win last month.

title: Joe Jonas tells fans not to believe anything if 'you don’t hear it from these lips'
description: Joe Jonas appeared to address internet speculation that he leaked negative press about his wife, Sophie Turner, after he filed for divorce last week during the Jonas Brothers' concert Saturday night.

title: Biden insists he’s not trying to 'contain' China as he courts Beijing’s rivals
description: President Joe Biden sought to downplay friction with China and insisted he is not trying to constrain the country’s rise in neighboring Vietnam.

title: Escaped Pennsylvania killer spotted again and has changed his appearance, police say
description: Escaped prisoner Danelo Cavalcante has been spotted again and has changed his appearance, police said early Sunday as they try to narrow in on the Pennsylvania fugitive.

title: Chuck Todd hands off Meet the Press to Kristen Welker
description: In his final broadcast as the moderator of Meet the Press, Chuck Todd talks to Kristen Welker about her experience as a reporter and his advice in the moderator chair.

title: Biden and Trump are tied in the polls. Democrats have mixed feelings about it.
description: Donald Trump is polling even with President Joe Biden in a likely 2024 rematch, sparking mixed feelings among Democrats 14 months from Election Day.

title: California Gov. Gavin Newsom would make an 'interim' choice if Dianne Feinstein vacates her Senate seat
description: California Gov. Gavin Newsom said he would not select any of the candidates running to replace Sen. Dianne Feinstein, if her seat becomes vacant.

title: After his suicide, a man’s family says Ozempic should carry a warning label
description: In the months before his death, Anthony seemed in good spirits: He had recently proposed to his girlfriend and been promoted at work.

title: Trump’s post-presidential office is hiding in plain sight
description: Donald Trump likes to put his name on everything — except his taxpayer-funded post-presidential office here on North Flagler Drive.
